## 7. Tech Stack

* **Protocol & Chain**

  * Hedera Hashgraph
  * Hedera Token Service (HTS)
  * Hedera Consensus Service (HCS)
  * Hedera Smart Contract Service (EVM compatible)

* **Smart Contracts**

  * Solidity (Farm Vault, Farm Factory)

* **Backend / API**

  * Node.js / TypeScript (planned)
  * Hedera JS/TS SDK

* **Frontend**

  * React / Next.js (or similar)
  * WalletConnect / HashPack integration (TBD)

