## 8. Getting Started (MVP Plan)

> ‚ö†Ô∏è This section will be updated as implementation progresses during the hackathon.

### 8.1 Prerequisites

* Node.js 20+
* pnpm / yarn / npm
* MetaMask / HashPack (for testnet)
* Hedera testnet account + funds

### 8.2 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/mybitcoin-farm.git
cd mybitcoin-farm

# Install root dependencies (if using monorepo, adjust to /frontend /contracts etc.)
npm install
```

### 8.3 Environment

Create `.env` (or `.env.local`) with:

```bash
HEDERA_NETWORK=testnet
OPERATOR_ID=0.0.xxxxx
OPERATOR_KEY=302e0201...
JSON_RPC_ENDPOINT=https://testnet.hashio.io/api
```

*(Add any other keys as contracts & APIs are wired up.)*

